room_title: Escape room "Wicked Witch's Castle" by Eludesions Escape Rooms in Phoenix
room_address: 2710 W Bell Road, Suite 1200, Phoenix, AZ 85053
room_description:
The Wicked Witch has hidden the Tin Man's heart, the Scarecrow's diploma, the Lion's medal, and the magical slippers. According to the legend, Dorothy should be emerging from her battered home any minute. You must locate all of the items and return them to their rightful place or the story will be altered and the Wicked Witch will be able to trap Dorothy in Oz forever.
The Witch was last spotted in the Haunted Forest, so we suggest that would be the best place for your journey to begin. Please hurry, you must prevail before the hourglass runs empty!
